# Task 1 – Business Objectives

## Project
Smart Library Request Workflow in ServiceNow

## Description
This task defines the business objectives for developing a Smart Library Request Workflow using the ServiceNow platform. The project focuses on automating library operations, improving book tracking, enhancing user experience, implementing secure role-based access, and generating reports for better decision-making.

## Objectives
- Automate library operations
- Improve book tracking
- Enhance student experience
- Increase librarian productivity
- Implement role-based access control
- Improve transparency
- Reduce manual errors
- Generate reports and analytics
- Improve resource utilization
- Support digital transformation

## Expected Outcome
A clear understanding of the project's business goals that will guide the design, development, testing, and deployment phases of the Smart Library Request Workflow.

## Technologies
- ServiceNow
- Flow Designer
- Workflow Management
- Access Control Lists (ACL)
- Users, Groups & Roles
- Reporting

## Status
Completed
